{"tid":2019662,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有藍屍表哥.....真係寧願冇表哥","createTime":"2020-05-16T12:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T15:01:14.000Z","uid":127575,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"bb38ca98a157921af29565af3dfc4a79d194474d","tid":2019662,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"同佢關係本身好好<br />\n就算同佢見面都好吹得水<br />\n佢都好好人<br />\n<br />\n但係自從社會事件發生後<br />\n佢facebook 日日分享港人講地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港G報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話示威者破壞香港<br />\n之後佢whatsapp send 短片比我，佢知道我深黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話美國利用香港人唱衰支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n( 當然我直接無視佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n最後佢facebook unfollow 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 非常歡迎 )<br />\n<br />\n佢本身深藍到發黑<br />\n撐美心 撐藍店 撐保皇黨 又好鍾意返支那旅行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一日同屋企人食飯排隊 ( 唔係藍店 )<br />\n突然間撞到表哥<br />\n佢同我屋企人打招呼<br />\n當然我都有同佢打招呼<br />\n唯獨佢唔會同我打招呼<br />\n甚至無視我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過冇所謂.......我做我自己繼續玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢同我屋企人吹完水之後<br />\n見到佢入咗間藍店食飯 ( 極深藍餐廳 )<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好多巴打絲打係咪都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f6e5caf161845490afc4446ef201c45b269609","tid":2019662,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a49a34d4bec08a542fc823810160e61d4b7d0d","tid":2019662,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=